.related vxvmhelp
.title Help: Volume Manager Visual Administrator Package
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The Visual Administrator's primary functions is to provide a
graphical user interface to the Volume Manager. In addition,
the Visual Administrator acts as an interface to serveral common
file system operations.

Volume Manager objects created by Visual Administrator interface
are fully inter-operable and compatible with those created by the
Volume Manager command-line interface.

If you install this package, you must also install the following
package: Volume Manager Package

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.

EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
